{"tid":1003142,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"差餉物業估價署公布去年12月本港私人住宅樓價指數報358.4點，按月跌2.39%，連續第5個月下跌，累計跌幅9.6%","createTime":"2019-01-31T12:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:25:06.000Z","uid":160028,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6682151c7decbb068a039e44dd46245459c5a34","tid":1003142,"uid":160028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"樓價指數連跌5個月<br />\n差餉物業估價署公布最新數據顯示，去年12月本港私人住宅樓價指數報358.4點，按月跌2.39%，連續第5個月下跌，累計跌幅9.6%。<br />\n<br />\n以5類單位面積劃分，各類單位樓價指數全數下跌，中小型單位(100平方米以下)售價按月跌2.46%；較大面積單位(100平方米或以上)售價則跌1.47%，按月跌幅最小為D類（1,076至1,721平方呎）大單位。<br />\n<br />\n5類單位樓價指數下跌<br />\nA類物業(40平方米以下)售價按月跌2.09%；<br />\nB類物業(40至69.9平方米)跌2.78%；<br />\nC類物業(70至99.9平方米)跌2.36%；<br />\nD類物業(100至159.9平方米)跌1.44%；<br />\nE類物業(160平方米或以上)跌1.49%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/87439/property_market/%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E9%BB%9E%E7%9D%87-%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8-%E5%98%89%E6%B9%96-3%E6%88%BF-%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF500%E8%90%AC/7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F87439%2Fproperty_market%2F%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%259D%2587-%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%25B8-%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25B9%2596-3%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E8%25B7%258C%25E7%25A9%25BF500%25E8%2590%25AC%2F7%2F&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=3be662e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/87439/property_market/%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E9%BB%9E%E7%9D%87-%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8-%E5%98%89%E6%B9%96-3%E6%88%BF-%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF500%E8%90%AC/7/</a>"},{"pid":"59db09265da9224a2c677544104006d486471e8e","tid":1003142,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"唔計喎"},{"pid":"27a09366fd3b1f53b837f03891b4100050c1476a","tid":1003142,"uid":105261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"其實啲業主。都肯減。但唔會好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c18a28901c59bee8476a834c583c9aa87fa201","tid":1003142,"uid":160028,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:18:28.000Z","msg":"9月話假跌睇10月，10月話睇居屋客回流有廿萬客，11月話居屋客要睇樓，12月話睇1月,1月話過年睇2月，2月話過緊年睇3月"},{"pid":"095a05501bf593e57d8f413d4a58363e5b01a626","tid":1003142,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"滯後唔計"},{"pid":"18d086ccdaacb8149f2800d3bab4f434f03a2e1b","tid":1003142,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"Big drop has come<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8506f470ab67a604e24c678f3d6662ec6ba2928","tid":1003142,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"CCL去年升5.66% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n居屋攪珠後，二手回投回升，新界西樓價結束連跌。中原城市領先指數CCL最新報174.37點，按周跌0.21%，連跌13周共6.55%。全年計則升5.66%。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181228/59080037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59080037&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=7570ec76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59080037&h=436bb5aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181228/59080037</a>"},{"pid":"3c3692b9f5bf6ac6464a9fd1821ee4fc6ba14623","tid":1003142,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"差估署私人住宅售價指數去年升 1.6%<br />\n<br />\n同CCL有4%差幅<br />\n<br />\n【新增業界回應】去年樓市吹淡風，差餉物業估價署公布數據顯示，去年12月私人住宅售價指數報358.4點，按月跌2.4%，惟跌幅較11月收窄，樓價已經連續5個月下跌，累計跌幅9.6%，指數重回去年1月水平。2018年全年樓價輕微上升，較2017年12月報352.7點，微升1.6%，為過去十年來升幅最少一年。至於租金指數同樣下跌，按月跌1.3%至193.3點，回到去年6月水平。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190131/59206346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59206346&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=ee2b07eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59206346&h=7389a14d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190131/59206346</a>"},{"pid":"8394b5e88aab25bac41c38197f626019b1dd0fb5","tid":1003142,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}